arts.ttl: Europa League: Twente down Malmo to record first win
arts.sum: FC Twente still have a chance of reaching the next round after a 3-2 victory over Malmo in Sweden. Twente had recorded some good results in the group stage so far but all of them draws and a first win had eluded them as they headed to Sweden knowing they had to get three points.
